---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import imagen_perfil from '../../../images/imagen_perfil.jpeg';
import { Download, HBlandas, Maletin, Medalla } from '../../icons/index';

---

<div class="text-center mb-2" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold dark:text-white text-text-light_secondary mb-4">Sobre <span class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6366f1] to-[#a855f7] bg-clip-text text-transparent">mí</span></h2>
 </div>
 <div class="max-w-full mx-auto flex flex-col items-center mt-2 mb-4 sm:mb-10 gap-2" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    </div>
 </div>
 <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-8 items-center">
    <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center md:justify-start" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <div class="relative w-48 h-48 sm:w-58 sm:h-58 aspect-square">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br dark:from-accent-purple/30 dark:to-accent-blue/30 from-accent-light-purple/30 to-accent-light-blue/30 backdrop-blur-xs border dark:border-white/10 border-light-border shadow-xl overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
              <Image 
                  src={imagen_perfil} 
                  alt="My personal picture" 
                  class="w-[170%] h-[170%] object-cover object-center"
              />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br dark:from-accent-purple dark:to-accent-blue from-accent-light-purple to-accent-light-blue opacity-20 blur-xl animate-pulse"></div>
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-6 sm: ml-0 md:ml-10 text-center md:text-left" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white text-text-light_secondary mb-2">Wayroon <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6366f1] to-[#a855f7] bg-clip-text text-transparent">Estrada</span></h3>
       <h4 class="text-xl bg-linear-to-r from-accent-purple to-accent-blue text-transparent bg-clip-text font-semibold mb-6">Desarrollador Backend</h4>
       <p class="text-pretty text-justify dark:text-primary-foreground text-primary-light-foreground text-base mb-8">Me llamo Wayroon Estrada, pero la mayoría me dicen Bayron, soy Ingeniero de Sistemas y desde que empecé la carrera estoy profundamente centrado en el desarrollo de soluciones modernas. Me apasiona el backend y las estructuras de datos. Aunque mi fuerte no es el frontend, soy capaz de crear diseños actractivos con el cliente y la experiencia de usuario.</p>
       <p class="text-pretty text-justify dark:text-primary-foreground text-primary-light-foreground text-base mb-8">Cuento con experiencia en el desarollo de software, he trabajado como freelancer creando aplicativos webs para pequeñas empresas y pequeños emprendedores, aumentando su presencia en internet y mejorando su experiencia de usuario. También cuento con experiencia adquirida en la empresa Ecopetrol en el área del análisis de datos dándole un valor importante a los datos para la toma de decisiones. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-8 mx-auto flex justify-center md:justify-start mt-2 md:mt-4 " style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Tf4Ry42YvZpCr8-lW6Gf_pZZURiP7IYp/view?usp=drive_link" download="CV - Wayroon Estrada" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex gap-3 items-center h-12 bg-linear-to-r dark:from-[#6366f1] dark:to-[#a855f7] from-accent-light-purple to-accent-light-blue text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/25 transition-colors duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <Download/>
          Descargar mi CV
       </a>
    </div>
 </div>
 <div class="h-full mt-10 md:mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 mx-auto md:px-20 lg:px-0 gap-6">
    <div class="group h-full" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <div class="relative z-10 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl h-full flex flex-col justify-start">
          <div class="absolute -z-10 inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 dark:opacity-10 dark:group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
             <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-white/10 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-6 mr-4">
                <Maletin/>
             </div>
             <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white dark:text-gray-300">+ 2 Años de experiencia</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
             <li class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 p-2 rounded-lg bg-linear-to-r from-accent-purple/20 to-accent-blue/20 dark:border-white/10 border-border-light border"><span class="text-sm flex-grow text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-200">Desarrollador fullstack</span><span class="text-sm min-w-max text-end text-white dark:text-gray-300">2 años</span></li>
             <li class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 p-2 rounded-lg bg-white/5"><span class="text-sm flex-grow text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-300 ">Análista de datos</span><span class="text-sm min-w-max text-end text-white dark:text-gray-400 ">1 año</span></li>
             <li class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 p-2 rounded-lg bg-white/5"><span class="text-sm flex-grow text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-300 ">Auxiliar de redes y telecomunicaciones</span><span class="text-sm min-w-max text-end text-white dark:text-gray-400 ">3 años</span></li>
          </ul>
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="group h-full" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <div class="relative z-10 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl h-full flex flex-col justify-start">
          <div class="absolute -z-10 inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-teal-600 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 dark:opacity-10 dark:group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
             <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-white/10 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-6 mr-4">
                <Medalla/>
             </div>
             <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white dark:text-gray-300">Graduado</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
             <li class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white/5 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full">
                   <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white dark:text-gray-300">Universidad de Pamplona</span><span class="text-sm text-end text-white dark:text-gray-400">2024</span></div>
                   <div class="flex flex-col mt-1"><span class="text-sm text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-300">Ingeniero de Sistemas</span></div>
                </div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white/5 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full">
                   <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white dark:text-gray-300">CertiProf</span><span class="text-sm text-end text-white dark:text-gray-400">2021</span></div>
                   <div class="flex flex-col mt-1"><span class="text-sm text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-300">Scrum Foundation Professional Certificate</span><span class="text-sm text-pretty text-white dark:text-gray-300"></span></div>
                </div>
             </li>
          </ul>
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="group h-full" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;">
       <div class="relative z-10 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl h-full flex flex-col justify-start">
          <div class="absolute -z-10 inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 dark:opacity-10 dark:group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
             <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-white/10 transition-transform group-hover:rotate-6 mr-4">
                <HBlandas/>
             </div>
             <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white dark:text-gray-300">Habilidades Blandas</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 w-full">
            <li class="col-span-2 rounded-full px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 text-white font-medium shadow hover:scale-105 transition text-center">
              Trabajo en equipo
            </li>
            <li class="col-span-1 rounded-full px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white font-medium shadow hover:scale-105 transition text-center">
              Autodidacta
            </li>
            <li class="col-span-1 rounded-full px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white font-medium shadow hover:scale-105 transition text-center">
              Proactivo
            </li>
            <li class="col-span-2 rounded-full px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white font-medium shadow hover:scale-105 transition text-center">
              Autodisciplina
            </li>
          </ul>
       </div>
    </div>
 </div>